OL,3,CAFC Bournemouth make club history by
OL,4,Cqualifying for European football
OL,6,FAFC Bournemouth have made history
OL,7,Fafter securing European football for
OL,8,Fthe first time in the club's history,
OL,9,Ffollowing Tuesday's 1-1 draw with
OL,10,FManchester City.
OL,12,FThe achievement was a fitting way to
OL,13,Fmark the final home game of head coach
OL,14,FAndoni Iraola, who was given a rousing
OL,15,Fsend-off at full-time ahead of being
OL,16,Freplaced by Marco Rose in the summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
