OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779286285
OL,3,CAFC Bournemouth make club history by
OL,4,Cqualifying for European football
OL,6,FAhead of kick-off, Bournemouth's
OL,7,Fstadium announcer made reference to
OL,8,Fneighbours Southampton being kicked
OL,9,Fout of the Championship play-offs for
OL,10,Fspying as he attempted to whip up the
OL,11,Fhome crowd.
OL,13,FJunior Kroupi raised the roof with a
OL,14,Fstunning 39th-minute opener.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
