PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779286285
OL,3,CAFC Bournemouth make club history by
OL,4,Cqualifying for European football
OL,6,FAfter being released by Marcus
OL,7,FTavernier, Adrien Truffert cut the
OL,8,Fball back from the left and 19-year-
OL,9,Fold forward Kroupi curled a stunning
OL,10,Ffinish into the right corner before
OL,11,Fcelebrating becoming the outright
OL,12,Fhighest scoring teenager in a debut
OL,13,FPremier League season, with a
OL,14,Fsomersault.
OL,16,FCity almost levelled within a minute
OL,17,Fof the restart when Cherries
OL,18,Fgoalkeeper Djordje Petrovic made a
OL,19,Fvital save to deny Nico O'Reilly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
