OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779286285
OL,3,CAFC Bournemouth make club history by
OL,4,Cqualifying for European football
OL,6,FEvanilson then tested visiting keeper
OL,7,FGianluigi Donnarumma before Guardiola
OL,8,Fattempted to spark a comeback by
OL,9,Fintroducing Phil Foden, Savinho and
OL,10,FRayan Cherki in an attacking triple
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,FBournemouth teenager Rayan, who was
OL,14,Fnamed in Brazil's World Cup squad on
OL,15,FMonday, struck the outside of the left
OL,16,Fpost following a corner as the contest
OL,17,Fremained in the balance going into the
OL,18,Ffinal quarter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
