PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779286285
OL,3,CAFC Bournemouth make club history by
OL,4,Cqualifying for European football
OL,6,FSubstitute David Brooks also
OL,7,Fsquandered two golden late chances to
OL,8,Fput the result beyond doubt, including
OL,9,Fstriking the right post.
OL,11,FThose misses were punished in the
OL,12,Ffifth minute of added time when Erling
OL,13,FHaaland swept home via the right post
OL,14,Fafter Rodri struck the left upright
OL,15,Fduring a goalmouth scramble.
OL,17,FUltimately, the goal did little to
OL,18,Fdampen the spirits of home fans, who,
OL,19,Fat the full time whistle, celebrated
OL,20,Fwildly a moment of history for
OL,21,FBournemouth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
